The app provides an AI chatbot that responds to user queries about the Code of Federal Regulations (CFR). The app is intended to be used as a guide and should not be relied upon as the sole source of information. Users should refer to the official Electronic Code of Federal Regulations (eCFR) for authoritative answers.

